</ul>

<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Sleepwalkers_(Koestler_book)">Sleepwalkers</a></p>
<ul>
  <li>examines personalities of people involved in transition from Ptolomaic Universe to Copernican Universe</li>
  <li>important because it shows how many people are “blind” to simpler theories (e.g. epicycles in Ptolomaic version)</li>
</ul>

<p>Songwriting</p>
<ul>
  <li>anything by Pat Pattison</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.patpattison.com">PatPattison.com</a></li>
  <li>tension and release of tension via rhyme choice</li>
  <li>good songs blend good lyric writing with good music writing (melody, chords)</li>
  <li>important for understanding choice of words and phrasing (even in technical documentation, IMO)</li>
  <li><a href="http://www.b-rhymes.com">B-Rhymes</a> (perfect rhymes are not always appropriate)
